sentences.english: Ziqiu ancient town, located in Changyang County in central Hubei Province, face to Qingjiang.
sentences.chinese: 古镇资丘，位于湖北省长阳县中部，临清江而立。

sentences.english: There are rich appreciating stone resources in Qingjiang river basin, which deserve to be developed and used in various ways.
sentences.chinese: 清江观赏石资源丰富，具有众多可开发应用的价值。

sentences.english: It connects Jiangxing Valley and Qingjiang River.
sentences.chinese: 它上连经行峡，下入清江。

sentences.english: Core wall rockfill dam is one of the representative types of the Shuibuya Project on the Qingjiang River .
sentences.chinese: 心墙堆石坝是清江水布垭水利枢纽的代表性坝型之一。

sentences.english: The indoor creep tests for the Qingjiang Gushubao landslide-zone soils have been carried out; and some creep data are obtained.
sentences.chinese: 通过对清江古树包滑坡滑带土进行室内流变试验。

sentences.english: Tianchikou landslide is a large unconsolidated deposit landslide in Geheyan reservoir area on Qing River.
sentences.chinese: 天池口滑坡是清江隔河岩库区一大型松散堆积物滑坡。

sentences.english: The main rivers in Yichang city are Yangtze River and Qingjiang River.
sentences.chinese: 宜昌境内主要河流的长江和清江。

sentences.english: Two sets of auto-monitoring system have been built up for Geheyan dam.
sentences.chinese: 清江隔河岩大坝已经建成两套安全监测自动化系统。

sentences.english: The scheme has been successfully applied in the Digital Qing River Project.
sentences.chinese: 该方案已在“数字清江”项目中得到成功应用。

sentences.english: Qingjiang valley is rich in intangible cultural heritages.
sentences.chinese: 清江流域有着丰富的非物质文化遗产。
